<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA64">
<l>paraṉā mavaṉātal pāvippa rāki</l>
<l>luraṉā lorumūṉṟu pōtu maramēḻaṉ</l>
<l>ṟeytāṉaip puḷḷiṉvāy kīṇṭāṉaiyē yamarar</l>
<l>kaitāṉ ṟoḻāvē kalantu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If they considered that he was the highest,</l>
<l>would the hands of the immortals not join [and] worship</l>
<l>with strength, once three times, the one who that day</l>
<l>shot the seven trees, the one who tore the bird’s mouth?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
